{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/mrsa-in-primary-care/goals-outcome-measures/qipp-options-for-local-implementation/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"db6fe095-36c1-5949-87a9-e1c049f58234","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 2664a54b-128b-4fa4-a5a4-246f3b0d2d55 --><h2>QIPP - Options for local implementation</h2><!-- end field 2664a54b-128b-4fa4-a5a4-246f3b0d2d55 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item a16867bc-ef35-4e25-b752-5600c6682fda --><!-- begin field 1f477865-c2a0-40d5-ad35-11412f96e6d6 --><p>Antimicrobial stewardship: prescribing antibiotics</p><ul><li>Review and, if appropriate, revise prescribing and local policies that relate to antimicrobial stewardship to ensure these are in line with NICE guidelines on <a data-hyperlink-id=\"89c1f84b-bce9-4b70-b4f3-a982008ad50c\" href=\"https://www.nice.org.uk/guidance/ng15\"><u>antimicrobial stewardship: systems and processes for effective antimicrobial medicine use</u> and <u>antimicrobial stewardship: changing risk-related behaviours in the general population</u></a>.</li><li>Review and, if appropriate, optimise current prescribing practice and use implementation techniques to ensure prescribing is in line with NICE <a data-hyperlink-id=\"397f5d43-26b6-4149-90a1-a982008ad530\" href=\"https://www.nice.org.uk/about/what-we-do/our-programmes/nice-guidance/antimicrobial-prescribing-guidelines\"><u>antimicrobial prescribing guidelines</u></a> or Public Health England (PHE) <a data-hyperlink-id=\"dcc98122-ca85-4db8-b662-a982008ad64a\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/managing-common-infections-guidance-for-primary-care\"><u>guidance on managing common infections in primary care</u></a>, the Department of Health's guidance <a data-hyperlink-id=\"bbf2df05-d25f-4579-9e4f-a982008ad669\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/antimicrobial-stewardship-start-smart-then-focus\"><u>Start smart âˆ’ then focus</u></a>, local trust antimicrobial guidelines and the Antimicrobial Stewardship in Primary Care collaboration <a data-hyperlink-id=\"33116be8-b0b9-421c-878f-a982008ad692\" href=\"http://www.rcgp.org.uk/TARGETantibiotics\"><u>TARGET antibiotics toolkit</u></a>.</li><li>Promote the <a data-hyperlink-id=\"ff7defdb-2694-428d-9558-a982008ad6d1\" href=\"http://antibioticguardian.com/\"><u>antibiotic guardian call to action</u></a> and the <a data-hyperlink-id=\"6b77bf9d-9bb4-43ab-af3a-a982008ad963\" href=\"https://campaignresources.phe.gov.uk/resources/campaigns/58-keep-antibiotics-working\"><u>keep antibiotics working</u></a> campaign.</li></ul><p>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/mrsa-in-primary-care/references/\">NICE, 2018</a>]</p><!-- end field 1f477865-c2a0-40d5-ad35-11412f96e6d6 --><!-- end item a16867bc-ef35-4e25-b752-5600c6682fda -->","topic":{"id":"26f48611-f890-5112-aa26-bef13e5623e1","topicId":"c9e197be-4f79-4d67-bf67-2b2a8a137e03","topicName":"MRSA in primary care","slug":"mrsa-in-primary-care","lastRevised":"Last revised in October 2018","chapters":[{"id":"ba15ac05-528a-5474-8925-89cfea95b961","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"97d099f9-1263-51e7-8c71-fb82256182d3","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"f6df2380-e42f-563b-8f75-a588376e1da7","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"530a7f74-53c2-5e4e-8c1d-ceb01bccf776","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"a17267d5-eb08-5126-9312-b78fee4494a2","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"9537a389-c41a-5355-ac9c-9c56bba48a35","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"124fbaa7-2678-5958-b4be-d5f9be74c18a","slug":"goals","fullItemName":